hu.elte.txtuml.api

Class Region

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.elte.txtuml.api.StateMachine
      • hu.elte.txtuml.api.Region
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelElement
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ModelClass

    public abstract class Region
extends StateMachine
    Base class for regions in the model.

    Represents: region

    Usage:

    By the current implementation, Region might not be used directly as all model classes may have at most one region and that is represented by the ModelClass itself extending Region.

    Java restrictions:

    • Instantiate: disallowed
    • Define subtype: disallowed, use its subclasses, like ModelClass

    See the documentation of Model for an overview on modeling in txtUML.

    Author:
    Gabor Ferenc Kovacs
